<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200821/1353a107ac654198b62b36d470513b15.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>3、俯身后抬腿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200821/c7226fe855c5402ba311ebee7113d86c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>4、俯身后提臀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200821/b71ed2fdbf1348febecd636d2b973a27.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>5、臀桥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200821/fa2eefeba5d749abbba68b150483a3dc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
